Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This white sausage is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it good...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Dieter, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you don't start eating, Dieter's \N going to have everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only regulars come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone new comes in...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Otto here will chase them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, business isn't getting any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who ordered the spaetzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set up a cot in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll sleep fine if you can stand the rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be brusque, but he's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, you can't fight on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:00:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've even arranged a room for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't saved me back there, \N I'd be in a morgue by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can only eat such good food when I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've contacted Dr. Gillen as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was relieved to hear that we found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He also put an ad in the paper with a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's reminisce about our cheating."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why didn't you contact him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...didn't want to drag him into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you need most are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you said you've been watching me all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Richard Braun's case...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The case where he shot a young serial murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while he was still with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was reading the article about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Dieter saw the picture of the one \N who got shot and told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that he had been at Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinderheim 511?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an orphanage in East Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rather special one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter's foster father was a former official there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept a large number of pictures \N of the children who were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what of that orphanage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan had been there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that the boy Richard shot \N and Johan are somehow connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here hoping to learn more about that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Richard passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you at his grave in the cometary, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like he brought you to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well to have made it this far on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will prove your innocence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan is right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have the photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have left it in my office!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Showing you Johan's photo would have \N cleared everything up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who came after you probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he probably destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said his name was Hesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He and his wife both came in for counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked up his information and checked \N out the address he gave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but nobody named Hesse lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan is right in front of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's in front of us, we can see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can clearly see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:22.92,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(217,200)\pos(354,341)}Into the Daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thalbach & Schuwald AG...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.44,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,39)}AG = Aktiengesellschaft = Corporation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This company is at the center of \N Schuwald's financial group.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, Schuwald has started appearing \N more than he used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around this time of day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he visits the companies he's affiliated with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something Richard discovered while he was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only this company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but every company in the financial group...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has started to grow after he began visiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since a certain young man became \N Schuwald's right hand man, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man in the wheelchair is Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the one pushing him is Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?  Were we mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've seen Johan in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drag everything out into the daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the only time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the only time we can prove your innocence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for now, hide yourself in the attic of Otto's restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, your innocence will be proven!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard's file was around here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I brought it back home with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your battle for revenge will soon be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've cornered Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've found Dr. Tenma, a definitive witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is find a witness from \N the night Richard was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can prove that Johan was with Richard that night!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fahren, the student who claimed to be Schuwald's \N son and committed suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To determine whether Johan took \N him to see that prostitute...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we only need to find her, and \N the proof will be established!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not only that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we dig into the past of the people \N who claim to be Johan's parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll know who Johan really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we've already found Johan Liebert's grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've completely entangled "Johan" in our net!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remind me of Richard when I look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're carrying all the justice in the world on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have Dieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have Dr. Gillen and me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should get a good night's sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...didn't want to get him involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've seen Johan in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the only time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Reichwein speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, it's Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was just about to call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way over right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Tenma doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's currently at the hiding place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him not to leave that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That his...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma's reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for going after Johan isn't to \N prove his innocence, but to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like to think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was worried about that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma... told me to come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma's going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Reichwein, please stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma's going to become a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop here for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Doctor.  Please listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just getting to the good part!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can take your time and tell me about it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story about how I killed the third woman is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of sound do you think \N she made when I strangled her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman!  She was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go, Tenma...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally meet, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Lunge, from the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard some rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've arrested several of the serial murderers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who are serving as my research subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've read your book as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a wonderful book.  "An Introduction \N to the Transcendental Criminal Psychology."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:13:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No other publication delves so deeply into the heart of a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the third chapter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The inquiries on Heinz Kaul from pages 262 to 294.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I especially liked how you concluded \N that the killer's childhood trauma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...led to his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very familiar with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored that you read it so carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My method of investigation also involves peering into the mind of the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and by becoming the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have a lot of experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever have some free time, \N I'd like to talk more about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we both don't have much time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll ask you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll ask you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been going to Munich quite \N often lately, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I won't take up much of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're meeting with the psychological \N counselor, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he was a teacher I admired when I was in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were at Düsseldorf University...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you went to Düsseldorf University...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was a rather excellent neurosurgeon \N in your class, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get to meet with Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's reminisce about our cheating. Rudi."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From May 1st to May 22nd...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you put this three-line message in all the \N major newspapers throughout the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought that esteemed \N people like you and Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would have cheated when they were students.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be nice to have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't friends with Dr. Tenma when we were students.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last May in Oder Park...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with your help...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Velbert police had Dr. Tenma surrounded \N and almost captured him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was because my wiretap malfunctioned, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One can infer that you assisted in his escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three murders at Eisler Memorial \N Hospital in Düsseldorf...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The patient murdered at the construction site...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murders in Heidelberg...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The middle aged couple murders \N occurring all over Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...were all done by someone other than Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the conclusion that I, a criminal psychologist, \N have come to after interviewing Tenma in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on the move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he run?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's innocent, why does he run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't he tell you where he is \N going, even though you're friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have evidence that he's not the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This paper analyzes all the information about the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This took a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The unnatural death of a young man named Fahren, \N who claimed to be Schuwald's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The unnatural death of former police officer Richard \N Braun, who was investigating the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trouble caused by those scrambling to become \N wealthy Schuwald's illegitimate son...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the center of everything lies a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is the same as the one Tenma \N claimed was the true killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan Liebert...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, a person of the same gender and name...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was found in a grave in Brunthal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh top of that, Dr. Reichwein, who took \N over Mr. Braun's investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was also targeted by someone the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to prove that these cases are all connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he understands that best, \N Tenma went into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you move your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't mind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little tool for memorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From a psychological point of view...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it seems as though the uncertainty in your \N heart is revealing itself in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of my hand, I use my cassette recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everything recorded onto these \N cassettes is entirely objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the information memorized by your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is affected by your subjectivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably how you've always worked, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The memories created by that hand are absolute...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you never have any errors in judgment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:18:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your hobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live only for work, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever made a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're terrified of making a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To you, Tenma has to be the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else your identity will fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a picture of Johan Liebert himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you prove they are all lies told by Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this boy right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a student at the University of Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, he's one of Schuwald's secretaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I keep this photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting now, this is police business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I've made a very big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Dr. Tenma right now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He should be in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact the Munich police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Request an all-points bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma is in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sniper rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you are talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have gotten a call from Mr. Heitmeyer \N in a mountain retreat in Fussen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10,000 marks up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This order is somewhat difficult to fill, so it'll take a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, do something about that body of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you lay down the money \N and get the right equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll just be a pearl thrown before swine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next in the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reception party to be held next week \N for the Munich Electronics Expo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be located at the provincial Chamber \N of Commerce and Industry building.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Important economic leaders are already gathering there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the EU integration, the Bayern Industry will carry the New Media Network on it's shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be the largest trade fair ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:22:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a reception...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hans Georg Schuwald appeared for \N the first time in twenty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and was showered with applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Mr. Schuwald attended \N in his wheelchair, he looked well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and showed off his good health.
